review: Sooooooo.....It's Applebee's- you all know what you are gonna get there, right, because everything comes straight from the freezer.  But this review  is more on the parking situation--- why don't they have a PickUp/TO Go parking spot?  I have gone to pick up to-go orders here only to get cussed out by people in the parking lot and are acting like angry A-holes.  I will never go back to this location and Bayshore is pretty much a nightmare on weekends all together.
I'd go here if the other restaurants around wouldn't have a table - ort of as a last resort. Once seated..I'd only order buffalo wings and a bloody mary.  That's all..
I have never had good service or good food at this location. Every time I go in either my food is horrible, it takes way too long, the staff is rude, or all of the above
